snippet.title: Mobius Bands / Mobius Strips (TANTON Mathematics)
snippet.description: Everyone, at some point in one's life, simply must cut a Mobius band in half. This little video gives a tiny discussion as to what is going on when one does. I also offer here a devilish variation for additional hours of mathematical paper-cutting amusement.
